## Governance

This repository includes a governance scaffold installed by
[dxp-init](https://github.com/governancecommons/dxp-init) v{{validatorVersion}},
based on [Governance Commons](https://governancecommons.org) standards.

This scaffold makes the project audit-ready, evidence-ready, and control-mapped.
It does not certify regulatory compliance, SOC 2 readiness, EU AI Act conformity,
NIST AI RMF completion, or operational control effectiveness.

